airBrand.Name: Economy Saver
airBrand.airText:
Enjoy the ability to change your flight dates and earn twice as many miles when you book an Economy Flexi Saver trip instead!
You get: 1) Ability to change flight dates 2) 2 times as many miles accrued

Our Economy Class innovative design minimizes intrusion into your personal space even as the passenger in front reclines; while ergonomic styling of the seat further maximizes knee and legroom. It also features a headrest that can be adjusted as desired for greater support.
An easily accessible seatback-mounted handset, personal and non-intrusive reading light and in-seat power supply, are just some of the many intelligent touches designed with you in mind. (Applicable to most aircraft types)
Enjoy a sweet deal on Singapore Airlines

airBrand.Name: ECONOMY CLASS - SH
airBrand.airText:
Cathay Pacific Makes your Economy Class Experience Better than Ever
• A cradle mechanism in the seat back allows for 6 inches recline • Headrest with side wings adjusts four ways to provide maximum head and neck support • Signature Chinese dishes alongside wide range of cuisines from around the world • 9-inch touch-screen personal TV with hundreds of Audio and Video on Demand selections • On-board Power Supply for laptop or other device, and a USB port
* If the flight will be operated by another airline or due to operational requirements, the inflight product and service may be different.
Makes your Economy Class experience better than ever, beginning with your seat.

airBrand.Name: Economy Basic
airBrand.airText: Kick back and relax in the cosiest Economy Class seats. Be served by an award-winning cabin crew that is the epitome of Malaysian Hospitality

airBrand.Name: Economy Saver
airBrand.airText: Upgrade to Economy Saver to add flexibility, allow miles upgrades and increase baggage allowance on weight concept routes

EMIRATES PAID SEATS NOW BOOKABLE IN GALILEO Worldspan and Apollo paid seating launch dates to be announced shortly.
Economy Saver includes:
• Seating available at a fee* • Changes not permitted or at a fee • Non refundable both before and after departure • 35% flown miles earned • Mileage upgrade eligibility at time of check-in • Checked baggage included * • Hand luggage x 1 bag 7 KG • Complimentary Wi-Fi • Soft and Alcoholic refreshments • ICE entertainment
* Please refer to fare rules for full conditions

airBrand.Name: Economy Flex
airBrand.airText: Economy Flex offers FREE SEATING, additional flexibility and mileage accrual.

EMIRATES PAID SEATS NOW BOOKABLE IN GALILEO Worldspan and Apollo paid seating launch dates to be announced shortly.
Economy Flex includes:
• Free seat assignment • Changes permitted at a fee • Refunds permitted at a fee • 70% flown miles earned • Mileage upgrade eligibility • Checked baggage included * • Hand luggage x 1 bag 7 KG • Complimentary Wi-Fi • Soft and Alcoholic refreshments • ICE entertainment
* Please refer to fare rules for full conditions

airBrand.Name: Economy Super Saver
airBrand.airText:
Enjoy the ability to change your flight dates and earn 5 times as many miles when you book an Economy Saver trip instead!
You get: 1) 5 times as many miles accrued

Our Economy Class innovative design minimizes intrusion into your personal space even as the passenger in front reclines; while ergonomic styling of the seat further maximizes knee and legroom. It also features a headrest that can be adjusted as desired for greater support.
An easily accessible seatback-mounted handset, personal and non-intrusive reading light and in-seat power supply, are just some of the many intelligent touches designed with you in mind. (Applicable to most aircraft types)
Enjoy a super deal on Singapore Airlines

airBrand.Name: Economy Saver
airBrand.airText: Upgrade to Economy Saver for the flexibility of changing your dates for a fee

The best inflight entertainment, selection of fine international cuisine, and warm Arabian hospitality. Welcome to Etihad Economy Class.
• 50% of Etihad Guest miles • Refer to fare rules for Refunds/Changes • Hand baggage x 1 bag at 7kgs • Upgrade eligibility • Neck pillows and soft fleece blankets • Tasty hot meals with a choice of three main courses, with vegetarian as standard • On board Cafe offering light snacks and a choice of teas, coffees and hot chocolate • Flying Nanny on board offering parents a helping hand on long-haul • Hundreds of hours of on-demand entertainment, on 10.6" screen with noise reduction headsets • Connectivity on board: Wi-Fi and mobile services • A range of connection ports at each seat, including USB and laptop power supply • Amenity kits with socks, eyeshades, earplugs, toothbrush and toothpaste on all long-haul and overnight flights • Complimentary luxury coach services between Dubai / Al Ain and Abu Dhabi International Airport • US Preclearance facility at Abu Dhabi Airport to pre clear US Immigration before guests board their flight to the US
